{"tid":17753,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"美女囚勾結奸夫謀害親夫 今執行死刑","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:13:53.000Z","uid":12709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a588ffd5744719a9190956239558c5127ab8a31b","tid":17753,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"美國喬治亞州政府今日對一名女囚吉森達娜(Kelly Renee Gissendaner)執行死刑，在當地時間周三凌晨12時21分宣告死亡，她也成為喬治亞州自1945年來，第1位執行死刑的女囚犯。<br />\n<br />\n據《美聯社》報導，吉森達娜在1997年2月犯下謀殺丈夫道格拉斯(Douglas Gissendaner)，她和當時的男友歐文(Gregory Owen)合夥，謀害親夫，最後歐文被判無期徒刑，他可在2022年申請假釋。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，吉森達娜原定在今年2月執行死刑，卻因天氣因素作罷。之後預定延至3月，卻因執行死刑的注射藥物有問題，而再次延期，今日吉森達娜正式伏法。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/110237_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F110237_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=64d4f3cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0c97719831c7f2e34ccd333e40e4a4b020efec3","tid":17753,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"正皮引伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7720c3ef8169bdc94177b12a574ee1dae8477b9","tid":17753,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"呢件咁既野都有婚外情"},{"pid":"e0720118563539e03b6936d3450d584735409d07","tid":17753,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ea8bf73df473341fa21d2fb42151d50bfc283d","tid":17753,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"有少少似American Horror Story果個"},{"pid":"312bcf47db9f25c4a5711a83385d70b4600833f7","ti